snippet.title: Steam #NextFest Vampire Therapist Livestream and Developer Chat
snippet.description:
This was originally broadcast on Steam on 6/11/2024. 

Join Little Bat Games developer Cyrus Nemati as he guides the audience through the demo for Vampire Therapist. Demo available on Steam!
